{"article_id":"BPjCGLYBGl3FO53W","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Trouble with the HealthCare.gov site appears to be so widespread","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that the Obama administration has opened the door","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"for Americans to circumvent the site altogether .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Under a plan","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"announced Friday by the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"the government would allow people to deal directly with insurance companies instead of through the federally run exchange website .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"The move comes","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"as the administration 's self-imposed Nov. 30 deadline","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"for fixing the site","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"is just days away ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"and officials acknowledge","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"it may not be fully operational by then .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The pilot program","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"announced by CMS","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"would initially launch for residents in Ohio , Florida and Texas ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"and is the latest effort","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"to give users an alternative to the troubled site .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"\" This is one more way","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"we are working","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"to offer consumers a variety of ways","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"to enroll in affordable coverage , \"","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"agency spokeswomen Julie Bataille said","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"in announcing the pilot project .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"\" By strengthening the multiple channels","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"to enroll in quality , affordable coverage ...","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"we are ensuring","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that every American","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"who wants it","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"can gain access to these new coverage options . \"","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"Bataille said","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that direct enrollment has \" been there from the start. \"","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"But the option was limited by the website problems ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"which have been fixed to the extent","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"that insurance companies can now send applications to the site","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"to assess enrollees ' eligibility for coverage and potential discounts on premiums ,","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Though the option could help Americans","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"frustrated by the HealthCare.gov ' s crashes , slow response times and other problems ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"it is another acknowledgement that the site probably will not be working for everybody by the administration ' s Nov. 30 deadline .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Officials originally vowed to fix the site by then .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"As the extent of the site 's problems became apparent ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"officials lowered the bar on that goal","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"-- vowing instead to significantly improve the site by the end of the month .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"White House spokesman Josh Earnest said Monday","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"that improvements to the site are on schedule ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"including faster response times ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"and that it should be able to handle 50,000 concurrent users .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"`` If there are more than 50,000 people","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"trying to use the website ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"individuals can choose to receive an email from CMS","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"when the traffic on the website has been reduced , ''","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"Administration officials have also been encouraging Americans to submit written applications ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"contact call centers","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"or visit sign-up centers","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"to enroll for insurance .","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"They continue to say","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"the site will be working smoothly by the end of the month for \" a vast majority of Americans. \"","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"And last week , they extended the enrollment deadline from Dec. 15 to Dec. 23","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"to get insurance coverage","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"starting Jan. 1 .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Americans ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"who are required to have insurance under the president ' s 2010 health care law ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"must enroll by the end of March","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"or face a tax penalty .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"In another development , GoHealthInsurance.com announced Monday","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"that it has become the first private insurer","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"to integrate with the so-called Federal Data Service Hub","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"-- -","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"which includes IRS , citizenship and other personal information .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"So Americans can now use that as well","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"to bypass the federal site","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"and enroll in health plans under ObamaCare","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"that kick in next year .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"The company also said","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"the process includes the capacity","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"to calculate the subsidies .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"As for the CMS announcement , Bataille said","depth":2},{"id":78,"text":"the pilot project will help improve the overall direct enrollment option","depth":3},{"id":79,"text":"because insurers and enrollees will provide federal officials with \" detailed feedback on their experience . \"","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":159,"left":156,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity